      <div class="product-content">
        <h2 style="font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 40px); margin-bottom: 20px;">How Does Final Expense Work?</h2>
        <p>Final Expense insurance is designed to cover end-of-life expenses. It offers a death benefit that helps cover funeral and burial costs, outstanding debts, and other related expenses.</p>
        <p>These policies are typically smaller in coverage and easier to qualify for than traditional life insurance — making them accessible and practical for people of all ages and health backgrounds.</p>

        <h3 style="font-size: 22px; margin: 32px 0 16px;">Is Final Expense Right for You?</h3>
        <p>Whether you're concerned about funeral costs, outstanding debts, or ensuring your family's financial well-being — Final Expense Insurance provides a compassionate solution that ensures your loved ones aren't forced to make difficult financial decisions during an already difficult time.</p>

        <ul class="product-features">
          <li>Smaller, manageable coverage amounts</li>
          <li>Easier to qualify for than traditional life insurance</li>
          <li>No medical exam required in most cases</li>
          <li>Covers funeral costs, burial, and related expenses</li>
          <li>Helps protect your family from unexpected debt</li>
          <li>Guaranteed acceptance options available</li>
          <li>Affordable premiums that don't break the budget</li>
        </ul>

        <a href="/pages/contact-us" class="btn btn-primary">Get Your Final Expense Quote</a>
      </div>
      <div>
